Tools for Research
Tools for Research
The following is a list of links that might be helpful for writing
research papers, finding research ideas, or locating information on
a research subject.
CS Research Resources
This is a listing especially for computer science.
Many of the resources are technical report indexes from various universities.
This department's technical reports are included in some of these indexes.
Math Resources
This is a listing especially for math.
Chemistry Resources
This is a listing especially for chemistry. Included is a "Web" periodic table
of the elements.
Yahoo
Yahoo is a searchable index of documents on Internet sites. It also contains
links to other Internet search engines.